{"tid":1549344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家後生仔就正啦,成日都玩人鏈","createTime":"2019-09-07T09:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T08:13:03.000Z","uid":119688,"like":4,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6255d1a4a1c1f6b2e3fae97f4171d9e9550ec54e","tid":1549344,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:40:19.000Z","msg":"日日都有得拖囡囡 大把異性識<br />\n唉 阿叔我連女仔手都未拖過啊<br />\n屌哂你地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b38e56ba971b944e503d7debf11d0ab2fb7ae5","tid":1549344,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bffcbe7552f07bf879b60e6245827860eec6c50","tid":1549344,"uid":293648,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:42:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>有線新聞 i-Cable News : 新聞台凌晨直播期間，在油麻地拍到「暴徒換上記者背心」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【嚴正澄清】有人在社交媒體流傳，有線直播新聞台凌晨直播期間，在油麻地拍到「暴徒換上記者背心」，並指控本台隨即移開鏡頭，試圖隱瞞事實，本台嚴正澄清如下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 片段拍到的男子，證實是now新聞台的工程人員。片段顯示，他一度脫下記者背心離開現場，幾分鐘後回來，再在其他記者協助下穿上背心。<br />\n2. 本台調動鏡頭，是準備新聞台下一節直播。片段中記者的聲音，只是回應直播室要求準備直播的指示。<br />\n<br />\n謹此嚴正聲明，有線新聞從不刻意迴避事實。對於有人完全不作查證，肆意發放虛假消息，毫無根據地攻擊本台的專業操守，本台深表遺憾。"},{"pid":"811683f2ca2ba3a2c0ac33aaebd73c7dac7d1d67","tid":1549344,"uid":257567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:43:20.000Z","msg":"好多男仔都係拖男仔喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9961268a770ae04532b29ad335b8b327b707188e","tid":1549344,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:47:32.000Z","msg":"你就算去人鏈都係penzoned"},{"pid":"26eaaa41580d9aaee40f8fe659a7cfa01265d15c","tid":1549344,"uid":254558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:48:00.000Z","msg":"元朗9.9七點半有人鏈<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dQdQeS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dQdQeS</a>"},{"pid":"1ec454d9c355a01391f1190a286e5a3a5ae0f48a","tid":1549344,"uid":119688,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"811683f2ca2ba3a2c0ac33aaebd73c7dac7d1d67","tid":1549344,"uid":257567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:43:20.000Z","msg":"好多男仔都係拖男仔喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QRdyfjb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQRdyfjb.jpg&h=af2dffc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VoZhGZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVoZhGZc.jpg&h=5ad18ee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌 嬲"},{"pid":"db92e400e12d281e45a2c87d9fa5e5e6384fef27","tid":1549344,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KKQwMq7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKKQwMq7.jpg&h=7228063d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0663fdeeb8a6ecc25f4c92168fca2a7eefec80f","tid":1549344,"uid":144323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T08:12:27.000Z","msg":"上次我拖個女仔個方法好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一嚟就十指緊扣咁拖<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣都無留意，之後先覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96d16a278d56a37f62bad1cb995f02772c762fd","tid":1549344,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T08:13:03.000Z","msg":"BLOCKED"}]}